Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US looks to Far East
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w96x
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 29 Mar 1981
Moves for better US-China and Japan relations, despite calls to curb imports. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.